originalText.text: Dr. Dennis was highly recommended to me and she was better then expected. I've had issues with my knee for decades and she explains what's going on with my knee with so much patience where I can understand exactly what's going on with. I am thrill with professionalism and I highly recommend this Doctor. I have gone else and I feel like I'm in a factory because I'm in and out with total confusion not with Dr. Dennis.

originalText.text: Dr Dennis is a star! She is thorough and takes patient care / successful outcomes very seriously. She has helped me address problems unrelated to her work such as billing, correcting errors in the system, and communicating with other medical staff to make sure my various ailments are treated. I feel very lucky that she was the person who performed my knee surgery. I have not had any complications and even my physical therapists are impressed by how skilled she is!

originalText.text: Dr. Dennis has been the best orthopedic doctor I’ve ever seen!   I highly recommend her for her  exceptional medical expertise and compassionate care. She is thorough and  explains everything.  Her attentive approach and genuine concern for patients create a reassuring and positive experience. I am grateful to have such a skilled and caring doctor along with her outstanding staff.

originalText.text: Dr Dennis is lovely and thorough. The only problem I had was I had booked an appointment at her Brooklyn location.. they have no X-ray machines and no boots (I have a broken ankle). Dr Dennis accommodated me the following day at her Noho location and I really appreciated that. Thank you Dr Dennis!

originalText.text: When trying to schedule my surgery, she missed messages I sent to ask about what to expect after and when the surgery was. Her coordinator wasn’t very helpful either and never answered her phone or called me back.  Decided to go with another doctor and was scheduled within two weeks vs Dr. Dennis office took over a month before anything started move. It was a waste of my time especially since it was an urgent surgery.
